    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Zerodha Advisory Limited. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Senior Financial Analyst to strengthen our Meerut-based team.\n\nAbout Zerodha Advisory Limited:\nZerodha Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Referral bonus program\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zerodha Advisory Limited!",
